      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for a sharp, linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis remains composed with a well-maintained MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Essential preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. While showing minor cosmetic patina from spirited use, the mechanical vitals and compression are strong, making this a technically sound platform for the purist.",
